From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


 Templates relating to Animals.    The pages listed in this category are templates. 
 This page is part of Wikipedia's administration and not part of the encyclopedia. 
show
 Further template category notes 

 This category contains pages in the template namespace. It should not be used to categorize articles or pages in other namespaces.  To add a template to this category: 
If the template has a separate documentation page (usually called "Template:template name/doc"), add [[Category:Animal templates]]to the <includeonly> section at the bottom of that page. Otherwise, add <noinclude>[[Category:Animal templates]]</noinclude>to the end of the template code, making sure it starts on the same line as the code's last character.

 

See also: Category:Animals
